<% layout('layouts/infoBoilerplate') -%>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 pt-20 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]">
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
                <i class="fas fa-cookie-bite text-[#fe424d] mr-3"></i> Cookie Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Understanding how we use cookies to improve your Stayzio
                experience.</p>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium tracking-wider uppercase">Last updated: August 30, 2026</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">

            <div class="lg:w-1/4 hidden lg:block">
                <div
                    class="sticky top-28 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-list text-[#fe424d]"></i> Contents
                    </h3>
                    <nav class="sticky-nav flex flex-col space-y-1">
                        <a href="#what-are-cookies"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">What
                            are Cookies?</a>
                        <a href="#how-we-use"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">How
                            We Use Cookies</a>
                        <a href="#types"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Types
                            of Cookies</a>
                        <a href="#managing"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Managing
                            Cookies</a>
                        <a href="#contact"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Contact
                            Us</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="lg:w-3/4 prose-content bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-gray-100">

                <div id="what-are-cookies">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> What are Cookies?</h2>
                    <p>Cookies are small text files that are placed on your computer or mobile device when you visit a
                        website. They are widely used by website owners in order to make their websites work, or to work
                        more efficiently, as well as to provide reporting information.</p>
                </div>

                <div id="how-we-use">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How We Use Cookies</h2>
                    <p>Stayzio uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to recognize you when you visit our
                        website, remember your preferences, and give you a personalized experience that's in line with
                        your settings.</p>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Seamless Experience</h4>
                        <p>Cookies help us keep you logged in and ensure that your booking process is as smooth as
                            possible by remembering dates, guests, and property preferences.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="types">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i> Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> These cookies are strictly necessary to provide you with
                            services available through our website and to use some of its features, such as accessing
                            secure areas.</li>
                        <li><strong>Performance & Analytics Cookies:</strong> These cookies collect information that is
                            used either in aggregate form to help us understand how our website is being used or how
                            effective our marketing campaigns are.</li>
                        <li><strong>Functionality Cookies:</strong> These are used to recognize you when you return to
                            our website. This enables us to personalize our content for you and remember your
                            preferences.</li>
                        <li><strong>Targeting/Advertising Cookies:</strong> These cookies are used to make advertising
                            messages more relevant to you. They perform functions like preventing the same ad from
                            continuously reappearing.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <div id="managing">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i> Managing Cookies</h2>
                    <p>You have the right to decide whether to accept or reject cookies. You can exercise your cookie
                        rights by setting your preferences in your web browser. Most web browsers allow you to control
                        cookies through their settings preferences.</p>
                    <p>Please note that if you choose to reject cookies, you may still use our website though your
                        access to some functionality and areas of our website may be restricted.</p>
                </div>

                <div id="contact">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have any questions about our use of cookies or other technologies, please email us at:</p>

                    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 mt-6">
                        <p class="mb-1"><strong class="text-gray-900">Email:</strong> <a
                                href="mailto:privacy@stayzio.com"
                                class="text-[#fe424d] hover:underline">privacy@stayzio.com</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>